  {
    "index": 3,
    "hash": "sI4OBcEFrajK7NFYtmpLsx5nwUo=",
    "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:27.000Z",
    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "# Adapter Package Key Source Files\n\nThe `packages/adapter/` package is organized around a small set of responsibility-specific source files that anchor the codebase:\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `src/channel/swarm-channel.ts` | Native `IChannel` implementation \u2014 outbox push + inbox pull via Swarm |\n| `src/channel/composite-factory.ts` | Routes `\"gql\"` / `\"swarm\"` config types to sub-factories |\n| `src/channel/create-composite-factory.ts` | `createSwarmSyncBuilder()` \u2014 wires into `ReactorBuilder` |\n| `src/channel/add-swarm-remote.ts` | Per-drive Swarm remote registration |\n| `src/channel/manifest-manager.ts` | User + drive manifest writes on Swarm |\n| `src/swarm-client.ts` | Bee SDK wrapper: upload, download, feeds, encryption, stamps |\n| `src/swarm-crypto.ts` | AES-256-GCM encrypt/decrypt with SWE prefix detection |\n| `src/wallet-signer.ts` | Deterministic key derivation from wallet signature |\n| `src/plugin/init.ts` | Browser plugin: Bee detection, stamps, wallet, events |\n| `src/plugin/sharing.ts` | Cross-user encrypted sharing + import |\n\nThe `src/channel/` directory concentrates all reactor-integration code, while `src/plugin/` contains browser/Connect-specific wiring.",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:27.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:27.000Z"
    }
  },
